      <h4>The Architecture of SARS-CoV-2 Transcriptome</h4>
      <p><img src="http://localhost:4000/images/publications/2020-Cell-a.jpg" class="img-responsive" width="33%" style="float: left" /></p>
      <p>SARS-CoV-2 is a betacoronavirus responsible for theÂ COVID-19 pandemic.</p>
      <p><em>D. Kim, J.-Y. Lee, J.-S. Yang, J. W. Kim, V. N. Kim, and H. Chang</em></p>
      <h5><a href="https://www.cell.com/cell/fulltext/S0092-8674(20)30406-2">Cell, 181(4):914-921.e10</a></h5>
      <p class="text-danger"><strong> </strong></p>
